leader = <space>

leader+w+v - split window vertically
leader+w+s - split window horizontally
leader+w+[h,j,k,l] - move to window in direction

leader+p - invoke fzf

leader+t - create new tab
leader+m - move to right tab
leader+n - move to left tab

CTRL+n - invoke multicursor on the word under cursor, add new cursor on the matched word
         then use commands such as c, s, I, A or press v to use normal mode commands

leader+A - search the codebase for the word under cursor
leader+a - enter string to be searched in codebase
leader+c - focus the CtrlSF window
leader+C - toggle open/close the CtrlSF window
p - preview file in CtrlSF window
